  "description": "A wide-angle shot depicts a cityscape dominated by a large suspension bridge stretching across a body of water. The bridge features a grey-blue color, with cables supporting the roadway. The city skyline is dense with modern skyscrapers and buildings, exhibiting a variety of architectural styles. A hilly landscape is visible in the background, adding depth to the scene. The water is calm and slightly rippled, reflecting the grey sky above. The overall lighting is subdued due to the overcast conditions, creating a soft and diffused atmosphere.",
